<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><subLeg xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0 https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/schemas/hklm.xsd" xml:lang="en"><meta><docName>Cap. 311 sub. leg. C</docName><docType>cap</docType><docNumber>311C</docNumber><docStatus>In effect</docStatus><dc:identifier>/hk/cap311C!en</dc:identifier><dc:date>2024-08-18</dc:date><dc:subject>legislation</dc:subject><dc:language>en</dc:language><dc:publisher>DoJ</dc:publisher><dc:rights>the Government of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region</dc:rights></meta><main xml:lang="en" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0 https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/schemas/hklm.xsd"><docTitle id="ID_1438402966446_001" name="shortTitle" reason="inEffect" status="operational" temporalId="shortTitle" startPeriod="2018-06-28">Air
            Pollution
            Control
            (Smoke)
            Regulations</docTitle><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">(<ref href="/hk/cap311/s43">Cap.
                311,
                section
            43</ref>)<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></enactingFormula><commencementNote>[1 October 1983]</commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="/hk/2018/er3">E.R. 3 of 2018</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438402966446_003" name="s1" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2018-06-28" status="operational" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><heading>Citation</heading><content>These regulations may be cited as the Air Pollution Control (Smoke) Regulations.</content></section><section id="ID_1438402966462_002" name="s2" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2018-06-28" status="operational" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><heading>Interpretation</heading><leadIn>In these regulations, unless the context otherwise requires—</leadIn><def name="ApprovedDevice"><term>approved
                device</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">認可器件</term>) means a device specified in the
                <ref>Schedule</ref>;</def><def name="DarkSmoke"><term>dark
                smoke</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">黑煙</term>) means smoke which, if compared in the
            appropriate manner with the Ringelmann Chart or an approved device, would appear to be
            as dark as or darker than shade 1 on the Ringelmann Chart;<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1990/ln289">L.N. 289 of
                1990</ref>)</sourceNote></def><def name="RingelmannChart"><term>Ringelmann
                Chart</term>
                (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">力高文圖表</term>) means a shade chart of the type known at
            the date of commencement of these regulations as a Ringelmann Chart;</def><def name="Smoke"><leadIn><term>smoke</term>
                    (<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">煙</term>、<term xml:lang="zh-Hant-HK">煙霧</term>)
                includes—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438411862468_019" name="a" temporalId="s2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>dust or fumes; and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411862468_027" name="b" temporalId="s2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>soot, ash, grit or gritty particles emitted in smoke or steam.</content></paragraph></def></section><section id="ID_1438402966477_001" name="s3" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2021-10-07" status="operational" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><heading>Restrictions applicable to dark smoke emission</heading><leadIn>An owner of any premises who operates any chimney or relevant plant in such a manner
            that any dark smoke is emitted for more than 6 minutes in any period of 4 hours or for
            more than 3 minutes continuously at any one time, commits an offence and is
            liable—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438411862483_022" name="a" temporalId="s3_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>on first conviction, to a fine
                at
                level 4 and in addition to a fine of $100 for every one quarter of
                an hour during the whole or any part of which such offence is knowingly and wilfully
                continued; and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411862483_030" name="b" temporalId="s3_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>on any subsequent conviction, to a fine
                at
                level 4 and to imprisonment for 3 months and in addition to a fine
                of $100 for every one quarter of an hour during the whole or any part of which such
                offence is knowingly and wilfully continued.</content></paragraph><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/1990/ln289">L.N. 289 of
            1990</ref>; <ref href="hk/2021/er5">E.R. 5 of 2021</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438402966477_003" name="s4" reason="inEffect" role="regulation" startPeriod="2024-08-18" status="operational" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><heading>Amendment of <ref>Schedule</ref></heading><content>The
            Chief
            Executive may by order amend the <ref>Schedule</ref>.</content><sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2024/21">21 of 2024 s. 78</ref>)</sourceNote></section><schedule id="ID_1438402966493_001" name="sch0" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2018-06-28" status="operational" temporalId="sch0"><num value="0">Schedule</num><note class="align_right" role="crossReferences" type="inline">[<ref href="/hk/cap311C/s2">reg. 2</ref>]</note><heading>Approved
            Devices<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></heading><paragraph id="ID_1438411862515_034" name="1" temporalId="sch0_1"><num value="1">1.</num><content>Micro-Ringelmann Chart</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411862515_043" name="2" temporalId="sch0_2"><num value="2">2.</num><content>Miniature Ringelmann Chart</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411862515_052" name="3" temporalId="sch0_3"><num value="3">3.</num><content>Telesmoke</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438411862515_061" name="4" temporalId="sch0_4"><num value="4">4.</num><content>Smokescope</content></paragraph></schedule></main></subLeg>